2. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper specifically mentions graph database applications, indicating a focus on database-related research. 
3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes both shared-memory and distributed-memory algorithms for constructing the labeling structure, indicating a focus on distributed and parallel computing. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper mentions the computational challenges involved in constructing the labeling structure, indicating a focus on computational complexity. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) - The paper focuses on improving the performance of existing algorithms for constructing the labeling structure, indicating a focus on performance optimization.
